Undid revision 830885824 by [[Special:Contributions/Doug Weller|Doug Weller]] ([[User talk:Doug Weller|talk]])Klaus Klostermaier has a PhD in Indian History & culture. And you are Insisting that only opinions of archelogists can be included in this article. That is ridiculous. So i am reverting your edit-war. This is an article about Bhimbetka Cave shelters, and adding any content related to Bhimbetka rock shelters by any scholar, even a historian is fine. I am not making any claims in the article by this ciation, i am only adding an opinion by another scholar. If you have any citation from any other scholars which oppose opinions of Klaus Klostermaier feel free to add it in the article after this. Nobody is prohibiting you from adding citations which oppose the views of Klaus. Please visit the talk page [[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Bhimbetka_rock_shelters#Scholarly_citation_was_deleted_with_out_specifying_any_reason]] where i have explained why your claims are all wrong
